<!-- <title>Exploración</title> -->
<!-- <title component="metadata">Alineado con <xref ref="graVV-uniYY-secZZ" text="title"/></title> -->
<title component="metadata">Alineado con <xref ref="lec-VVVVVV" text="title"/></title>

<statement>
  <p>Escribe una situación que esté representada por el diagrama. Explica por qué el diagrama representa tu situación.</p>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-151731">
    <shortdescription>Diagram. Rectangle partitioned into 8 equal parts, 6 parts shaded.</shortdescription>
  </image>
</statement>

<solution>
  <p>[++++++++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p>Sample response: Noah walked <m>\frac{6}{8}</m> the length of the hallway. The diagram shows 8 equal pieces for the length of the hallway. Each one is <m>\frac{1}{8}</m>. Since 6 of them are shaded that represents the <m>\frac{6}{8}</m> of the hallway Noah walked.</p>
</solution>

</exercise>
